Market data updates are continually seen when a session is closed. This happens for all sessions that have orders that are terminated. if (status == SessionStatus.Done) {
    handleCompletedSession(sessionId, previousSessionOrderContext);
} else {
    handleRunningSession(sessionOrderContext, status);
} The above code in  server/apps/xpro-auctions-moc/moc-nucleus-simulator/src/main/java/com/mktx/auctions/moc/nucleus/simulator/processor/SessionStateUpdateProcessor.java  should take into account  Terminated  sessions.
